					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>These waves generally feature the same transmission: an unidentified pneumatic sound which occurs at a constant rate of 50 bpm.</p> </blockquote> <p>I know that this probably didn't mean what I first thought it was, and that in reality it would be close to 130ish BPM, but&#8230;</p> <p><em>my first thought was, &quot;it's a dubstep-emitting planet&quot;.</em></p> 
